{"tid":622070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【瘋搶自助餐】強國客圍廚房截食物 成盤擸走被嘲「餓咗幾百年？」","createTime":"2018-04-08T23:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T20:09:51.000Z","uid":47674,"like":161,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"29c37cfec0b5cdbf1eb26f92ea2e9790f7a1a999","tid":622070,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T23:28:34.000Z","msg":"記得入去睇個video<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【瘋搶自助餐】強國客圍廚房截食物 成盤擸走被嘲「餓咗幾百年？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180409/58047878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180409%2F58047878&d=mSnZCbuwGwLGEtgLd%2FnI7QCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=391d7b2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180409%2F58047878&h=9ec277c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180409/58047878</a><br />\n<br />\n盤盤皆空，要食靠搶！你吃過這樣瘋狂而絕望的自助餐嗎？內地媒體昨日曝光了一段影片，片中可見，在一間自助餐餐廳內，侍應才剛將一盤盤的食物搬出廚房，一群群客人便即蜂擁而上，將盤中食物掃光，有人更誇張，索性將整盤食物搬走獨享！<br />\n<br />\n從一段由在場客人拍攝的現場影片可見，侍應甫步出廚房，就被一眾客人圍堵，當中有老有嫩，一致鎖定他手上的盤子，舉起筷子、餐鉗甚至徒手搶食物，搶到了拔腿就走。侍應有意護着手中食物，縮着身子不斷退後，企圖將整盤食物送到桌面，可是客人們來勢洶洶，他最終無法突破重圍。一群沒有「圍堵」侍應的客人，就只好拿着空碟，圍在放滿空盤的自助餐桌附近，東張西望。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，事發於上周四（5日）傍晚，而涉事的餐廳則在江西南昌韓式汗蒸幕店「漢湯洗浴中心」內。拍攝影片的客人姚先生稱，因為洗浴中心推出了洗浴+自助餐超值套餐，當天店內人滿為患。「第一波6點半的時候，就從六樓排隊排到了五樓，然後一直堵在那裏」。<br />\n<br />\n而這「空前盛況」亦使自助餐的食物供不應求，姚先生大吐苦水：「裏面吃東西就跟搶一樣的，所有的東西，食物一上來，服務員剛端進來，還沒有上餐桌，（客人）就已經上去搶了」他還說：「有的客人直接從服務員手上，把一盤子直接端走了，像瘋了一樣的，人太多了！」"},{"pid":"9279dbb281242436452a0eb735c678644ecc5e41","tid":622070,"uid":511,"like":63,"dislike":2,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T23:36:16.000Z","msg":"段片真係笑到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1485df345f55797688ce1032ac2737b3ac99d54f","tid":622070,"uid":42188,"like":137,"dislike":0,"score":137,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T23:53:28.000Z","msg":"$58一位清過期食物/黑心食物，正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707b9a78cc5c55258d539aeb4b08d2866efcfd87","tid":622070,"uid":6030,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:00:26.000Z","msg":"諗返起薩拉熱窩砵仔糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b0959d21415eaa7e515d8b4e7906b81fada6dd","tid":622070,"uid":95942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  笑到仆街"},{"pid":"0bbcbc7a8407560fd0b7dacc336b7b8e4a3d4f7c","tid":622070,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:11:26.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"bcdd1f513f68dbb6f0d85783ea0dce2f8f1e941f","tid":622070,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a06943d2f96e63fc0aba2e1ed939d40822de0e","tid":622070,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38bfcb30b1237532bb7b34578fa36bdfc5afd293","tid":622070,"uid":72343,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:34:32.000Z","msg":"餓狗搶屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ce9db718e2e5af91c277d4755a6e74595f7d20","tid":622070,"uid":119347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:35:51.000Z","msg":"餓狗搶屎"},{"pid":"087f87332a762afde901cf5e52f63ce0b640fb7c","tid":622070,"uid":170044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:38:22.000Z","msg":"餓狗搶屎"},{"pid":"6eda27efa0b